#
# CHART ANALYSIS (Live Data):
# - Current: $1.19 | VWAP: $1.16 | EMA(21): $1.19
# - ADX: 18.6 (WEAK - needs to climb above 20 for trend)
# - Status: Consolidating, waiting for momentum
# - Range: $1.10 - $1.25 | Recent high: $1.35
#
# STRATEGY:
# Wait for momentum indicators to align. ADX currently weak at 18.6,
# need it above 18 (lowered threshold) with bullish MACD and DI.
#
# ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  MOMENTUM STACK REQUIREMENTS                                              ║
# ║                                                                           ║
# ║  Current Status:                                                         ║
# ║  ✓ Price > VWAP ($1.19 > $1.16) - CONFIRMED                              ║
# ║  ? MACD > Signal - PENDING                                               ║
# ║  ? +DI > -DI - PENDING                                                   ║
# ║  ? Momentum > 0 - PENDING                                                ║
